TITLE: Episode 111 - A Journey Into Mystery with False Reality Check (with Surprise Guest Brad Binkley)
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by our new friends, Buffalo Rambler and Leggs of False Reality Check. A couple who are radically reconsidering their base assumptions and journeying through parts unknown. Join us as we pick their brains. You're going to have a great time. Also, Loki Odinson (as portrayed by Brad Binkley) joins us.
